front.title: CZ-4
front.gametext: Opponent may not 'react' to or from same site. You may 'react' to a battle or Force drain at same or adjacent Jabba's Palace site by deploying (at normal use of the Force) one non-unique alien to that site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Very common communications droid. Some have been modified to be defense drones. Programmed to warn their masters of an imminent attack.
